  "text": "The zero sequence components corresponding to each stator set are phase-shifted by 30 electrical degrees; they are separately computed with a simple logic algorithm. This algorithm reconstructs the zero sequence component of one three-phase set [CITATION_1] as the voltage command which has an intermediate value, as shown in Fig. 6 for the abc set.",
